name: Doct - Doctor Management Web App UI KIT
description: Doctor web app is the modern web app design for healthcare, specifically designed for doctor web applications. It is a complete solution for doctors to manage their patient appointments, patient details and also manage billing of particular patients. This UI KIT can be used for any health-related website such as doctor dashboards, clinics, hospital management software, online doctor app, doctor consultation centers, online doctor appointment app, medical laboratories, dental clinics, pharmacies management app, etc. Special priority has been given to visual hierarchy and consistency covering all the pages of this web app. All Screens & components are designed in high-quality details in Figma, XD, Sketch
